Employee Attendance app goals
1) Create records of employee and store their information.
2) Allow daily Log-in and log-out.
3) Allow admins to adjust attendance.
4) Check weekly hours of staff.
5) Add new employee.
6) Reporting functionality. 

Front page of app will show current employee record with the link to other forms.
Everything will be accessed via main page. There will be admin users who will have added functionality. 
Front page will also show current record of employee who are logged-in.
Rostering system not included.
